('100.00', 'The entrance fee structure for commercial vehicles visiting national parks is based on the capacity of the vehicle you arrive in, not the\nnumber of passengers. This fee is valid for 7 consecutive days with the same company and the same passengers.', 'Commerical Vehicles (Capacity of 16 to 25 passengers)', 214),
('200.00', 'The entrance fee structure for commercial vehicles visiting national parks is based on the capacity of the vehicle you arrive in, not the\nnumber of passengers. This fee is valid for 7 consecutive days with the same company and the same passengers.', 'Commercial Vehicles (Capacity of 26 or more passengers)', 215),
