('30.00', 'This permit allows all persons traveling with the permit holder in one single private, non-commercial vehicle (car/truck/van) to leave and re-enter the park as many times as they wish during the 7-day period from the date of purchase.', 'Death Valley Entrance Fee - per vehicle', 237),
