('0.00', 'Admission to our museum, cafe, and gift store is free for all visitors.', 'Museum under the Gateway Arch', 331),
('7.00', 'How did they build it? Come see the award-winning film Monument to the Dream and find out! The film documents the construction and meaning of the Gateway Arch and is shown daily at Tucker Theater in the Gateway Arch Visitor Center. The film is a half hour long, and America the Beautiful park pass holders get a $3 discount.', 'Documentary Movie', 332),
