('0.00', 'The NPS does not charge a fee to enjoy the Ice Age National Scenic Trail, Some public lands such as state and county parks located along the Trail may charge entrance fees. Camping registration, permits, and fees may also be needed. Before your visit you should check with the local land manager regarding possible fees and registration requirements.', 'Fees', 426),
