('NPS Photo', 'The Front Porch, Garfield Home', 'Front porch of Garfield home showing red front door', 'The front porch of James Garfield\'s home was the scene of the first front porch campaign. The presidential candidate gave patriotic speeches and met with thousands of people who came to which him well during the summer and fall of 1880.', 'https://www.nps.gov/common/uploads/structured_data/3C8438A8-1DD8-B71B-0B1FAF95F1FC35BF.jpg', 1379),
