('NPS / Bob Roney', 'Rainbow over Half Dome', 'A rainbow over a mountain in the distance.', 'A hike up to Sentinel Dome rewards people with great views of the landscape around them.', 'https://www.nps.gov/common/uploads/structured_data/3C84C6CF-1DD8-B71B-0B1C7CB883AA8FB1.jpg', 2773),
