('NPS/Shane Carte', 'The Watchman', 'A triangular sandstone mountain overlooks green and yellow foliage. A cloudy blue sky is overhead.', 'The Watchman in Zion Canyon', 'https://www.nps.gov/common/uploads/structured_data/68BFC1AC-BF96-629F-89D261D78F181C64.jpg', 2794),
