('NPS', 'Zion Canyon Visitor Center', 'A sandstone and glass building surrounded by tall trees with a mountain behind it.', 'The Zion Canyon Visitor Center is a great place to stop to learn about the park!', 'https://www.nps.gov/common/uploads/structured_data/68D46E7D-A116-A443-ABA04AD1DD785208.jpg', 2796),
